<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e74c3c;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .activation-code {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e74c3c;
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .validity-info {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777777;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777777;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .contact-info {
            color: #3498db; /* Blue color */
        }
        .cool-sentence {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #27ae60; /* Green color */
        }
        .company-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello, <%= user.name %>!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us. Please use the following activation code to verify your email address:</p>
        <p class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></p>
        <p class="validity-info">This code is valid for the next 5 minutes.</p>
        <p>If you did not sign up for this account, please disregard this email.</p>
        <p class="cool-sentence">We're excited to welcome you to our community!</p>
        <p>To learn more about our services or if you have any questions, feel free to <span class="contact-info">contact us</span> at <a href="mailto:sachinandan.priv05@gmail.com" class="contact-info">sachinandan.priv05@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
           
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>